{
  "stem": "1929.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that, that, that was also-- you know, at that time, like, I got ice skates for my birthday.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father-- that was a very big deal, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- I wanted-- I was just dying to feel what it felt like to have steel-- because from then on I was-- before that, I was just ice skating with my shoes and things like that.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But to have ice skates.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I wanted to go to the park.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they said, nope.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No way can you go to the park.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You can't do it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You can't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I skated on the streets with other kids.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They just didn't want Jews in the park?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Is that why?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they-- so I understand they would beat you up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just any time that there were the two groups together, there would be violence.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think this, this was happening in 1938 and '39, because Hitler had, had even-- anti-Semitism was there any way forever in Poland, but it was worse at these years because Hitler had stirred up this anti-Semitism, too.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I heard it when-- I remember something-- I don't know if we had a radio or they went out and they bought one, this big Phillips radio.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Phillips was a big name in Europe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we listened to Hitler.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every time Hitler used make a speech, I would-- I would-- the family would be all gathered around the radio.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I would hear him, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I would distinctly hear this German talk and the, you know, heil seig, heil, and Juden this and Juden that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I understood.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I could-- I could sense it and I could feel the anger in his voice and the threats.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
